{"tid":2052661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［Share俾藍絲］葉劉淑儀關於 BNO 的說法才是真正的「搵人笨」","createTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T17:17:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c935c1af134b6b0d4bac13fca88c49e6a5dc68b4","tid":2052661,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-bno-%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84-%E6%90%B5%E4%BA%BA%E7%AC%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-bno-%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%2590%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AC%25A8%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=85e1c71c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B7%2591%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-bno-%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%2590%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AC%25A8%2F&h=8e5c93b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-bno-%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84-%E6%90%B5%E4%BA%BA%E7%AC%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯她在影片中卻如是說：「凡是去過英國的人都知道，如果六個月免簽到期，只需要走過英倫海峽，到法國再回來英國，就再有六個月免簽，如何外交部長出手？」她更以外傭出境一轉再返港就有新一輪免簽證為比喻，試圖將藍韜文的計劃矮化為「與現今政策無異」。<br />\n<br />\n如果信她，就真是被搵笨了。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，英國政府不是省油燈，為防止外藉人士非法工作或居留，無論是否免簽證者均會被審查，包括了解來訪目的及停留時期、是否有足夠財力應付停留期間及往返費用，更重要是：最近十二個月內，在英國累積停留期間，有否超過六個月。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，如果以免簽證方式去英國，在第一次停留滿六個月後，短期內第二次入境時，海關將對旅客進行更為嚴格的入境審查，如非特別原因（觀光、遊學、傾生意一貫免談），不得在十二個月內在英國境內累積停留超過六個月，「到法國再回來英國就無問題」一說，並不成立，除非這趟法國「旅程」，也是半年。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這都不是重點。如果有留心英揆約翰遜在《泰晤士報》的文章，以及外相藍韜文一向的說法，英國對 BNO 政策的最大可能（暫時只是可能）改變，其實是工作權（right to work）⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a0ac4c6eb90af6dad56ad972d60a4df685e15701","tid":2052661,"uid":153151,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"479cd6b2f102d759166765518c62cad18eb6aef8","tid":2052661,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0ac4c6eb90af6dad56ad972d60a4df685e15701","tid":2052661,"uid":153151,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ecf2e00ed1336271bc42e9b47187648331aac4","tid":2052661,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"有工作權即使照攞working visa已經係兩回事"}]}